<h2 id="when-to-use-each">When to Use Each</h2>
<h3 id="use-rdbms-when">Use RDBMS when:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Strong consistency, data validation, and complex relationships are required.<br />
</li>
<li>Data is structured with predictable schemas.<br />
</li>
<li>Transaction integrity is critical.<br />
Examples: Banking, payroll, inventory, e-commerce.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="use-nosql-when">Use NoSQL when:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Data model changes frequently or includes semi/unstructured data.<br />
</li>
<li>Massive scalability or real-time analytics are needed.<br />
</li>
<li>Speed and availability are prioritized over strict consistency.<br />
Examples: IoT, social media, content management, recommendation systems.</li>
</ul>
<hr />
